Guests can enjoy a swimup bar, a rooftop bar, and free breakfast during their stay.
Learn more.
Is parking available at Wyndham Danang Golden Bay?
Yes, free parking, secured parking, and street parking are available to guests.
What are some restaurants close to Wyndham Danang Golden Bay?
Conveniently located restaurants include F29 Golden Beef & Sky Bar, Mooniva River Club, and Quan Ho Tren Nui.
See all nearby restaurants.
Are there opportunities to exercise at Wyndham Danang Golden Bay?
Yes, guests have access to a pool, a fitness center, and a sauna during their stay.
Does Wyndham Danang Golden Bay have an airport shuttle?
Yes, Wyndham Danang Golden Bay offers an airport shuttle for guests. We recommend calling ahead to confirm details.
Does Wyndham Danang Golden Bay have airport transportation?
Yes, Wyndham Danang Golden Bay offers airport transportation for guests. We recommend calling ahead to confirm details.
Is Wyndham Danang Golden Bay located near the city center?
Yes, it is 0.3 miles away from the center of Nai Hien Dong.
Are any cleaning services offered at Wyndham Danang Golden Bay?
Yes, dry cleaning and laundry service are offered to guests.
